<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000608/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """The type of course and the approach described above make more convenient to select an assessment mechanism
different to the traditional final exam. A continuous evaluation methodology is here proposed for this course, based
on a set of short quizzes and exersices (problems) resolution .
The assessment of lab practices is based on the realization of a report (in pairs) will be also considered
If some quizzed are failled will be retrieved in a final exam at the end of the course"""@es ;
